src/serial/ll-src/prestream.f File Reference

Detailed Description

Pre-Stream and Strean steps for order parameter distribution function f and pressure distribution function g in the D2Q9 Lee-Lin multiphase LBM.

The pre-stream step is done in f and g, which are then streamed into fbar and gbar.

Directional differentials are evaluated using a second order switching differential scheme (biased/central). Other differentials are evaluated using a standard second order central differencing scheme.
